{"tid":1910568,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢方艙醫院一武漢肺炎患者出院後死亡","createTime":"2020-03-04T18:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T10:51:22.000Z","uid":140538,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"456585f0c61ba19822c3ca4e2daf0e540e2118e6","tid":1910568,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:21:12.000Z","msg":"3月4日，武漢礄口區的梅女士向澎湃新聞反映稱，自己的丈夫李亮，今年36歲，被確診為武漢肺炎患者，經治療，2月26日從方艙醫院出院，到指定的酒店康復點隔離，3月2日突然在康復點發病，送醫後不治。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3SibEa5CYuacNy8icK75N1txSMUvFS3sJa99aEhVibRdVtaoFHJRkCjSdSxxibb61OhHwInicxibTGFsSicMw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fyl6JkZAE3SibEa5CYuacNy8icK75N1txSMUvFS3sJa99aEhVibRdVtaoFHJRkCjSdSxxibb61OhHwInicxibTGFsSicMw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1&h=2e0a72b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梅女士提供的由武漢市衛健委開具的居民死亡醫學證明（推斷）書顯示， 李亮直接死亡原因為武漢肺炎，引起死亡的疾病或情況為呼吸道阻塞猝死、呼吸循環衰竭。 <br />\n<br />\n漢陽方艙醫院2月26日開具的出院證明顯示，李亮2月12日開始在漢陽方艙醫院住院，經過規範治療、專家組會診確認，符合武漢肺炎患者出院標準，准予出院。  出院證明提醒： 出院後請在社區單人單間隔離14天，如有不適，請立即聯繫社區負責人，必要時到指定醫院就醫。。<br />\n<br />\n梅女士稱，李亮出院後進行隔離觀察的康復點在武漢礄口區漢西三路維也納酒店。  她說，入住一兩天后，丈夫說自己嘴巴髮乾，胃有點脹。  3月2日上午，她再次與丈夫進行視頻聊天，丈夫說他不想吃東西，躺在床上沒有力氣，站都站不穩，並很快掛了電話。  梅女士非常擔心，再打丈夫電話就打不通了。 梅女士非常担心，再打丈夫电话就打不通了。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3SibEa5CYuacNy8icK75N1txSMcqb1x8RfUPmp0TAH3giaRibIPuhNg9vX0eVZFvOCAc8RCxhqNHMoYILQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fyl6JkZAE3SibEa5CYuacNy8icK75N1txSMcqb1x8RfUPmp0TAH3giaRibIPuhNg9vX0eVZFvOCAc8RCxhqNHMoYILQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1&h=2832c24b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3月2日上午10點多，李先生又接了她的視頻電話，此時醫生正好來查房，醫生告訴她，李先生可能是精神壓力大。 <br />\n<br />\n梅女士說，後來120把丈夫送去了最近的醫院，丈夫當天下午5點8分過世。<br />\n<img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3SibEa5CYuacNy8icK75N1txSMt1KCkJrgGCUEX4kTU1mBDK4OYozKkf77qicOOa3IQ9CKLgpj1hkiaFYg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fyl6JkZAE3SibEa5CYuacNy8icK75N1txSMt1KCkJrgGCUEX4kTU1mBDK4OYozKkf77qicOOa3IQ9CKLgpj1hkiaFYg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1&h=ef18cf94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據梅女士提供的多份書面材料顯示，其丈夫李亮的2月4日CT報告單顯示為&ldquo;雙肺感染，考慮病毒性肺炎&rdquo;； 經過治療後，2月23日CT報告單顯示，&ldquo;雙肺見散在多發密度增高影，大部分呈磨玻璃密度，部分呈網格樣改變，大部分位於胸膜下，雙肺下葉見小結節灶，最大徑0.4CM，建議隨診複查&rdquo;； 2月25日的出院小結顯示，經對症支持治療，患者李亮體溫正常3天以上，呼吸道症狀明顯好轉，連續兩次核算檢查陰性，無吸氧指末氧飽和度大於95%，病程超過14天，經專家組評估，准予出院。"},{"pid":"269935a4101c1526d8895ed9abd09644f8088fc3","tid":1910568,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:23:22.000Z","msg":"冰山一角 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c61912558cae01ae418c50b0ff33a6ca4ca872","tid":1910568,"uid":342527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:25:08.000Z","msg":"出院後死 數字就唔計入武肺<br />\n方艙理撚得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a958ebe549e6b6f128b2b84d24b6c44ee014383","tid":1910568,"uid":140538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"36歲<br />\n出院後得D在腸胃症狀,5日後過世"},{"pid":"e7715c9e4d69388c88628793ab6b374d61cfef06","tid":1910568,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:31:59.000Z","msg":"個名有兩個字一樣都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42431fcf9c4ee566e015fb02c59b9dca3f4422e1","tid":1910568,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60c61912558cae01ae418c50b0ff33a6ca4ca872","tid":1910568,"uid":342527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:25:08.000Z","msg":"出院後死 數字就唔計入武肺<br />\n方艙理撚得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:33:09.000Z","msg":"出院標準大躍進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1c236085eda6bbf9f9f7ebd5d7c884c72709e9","tid":1910568,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:37:23.000Z","msg":"BTW呢個新聞<br />\n澎湃首發 10分鐘刪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鳳凰轉發 10分鐘刪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/WIMkAq2olBMizCCr0aKRFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FWIMkAq2olBMizCCr0aKRFg&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIHwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=7b43ba69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/WIMkAq2olBMizCCr0aKRFg</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img9.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p250694660.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg9.doubanio.com%2Fview%2Fgroup_topic%2Fl%2Fpublic%2Fp250694660.webp&h=58da25fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85c06b843b753869961930c59bdfb69b60054675","tid":1910568,"uid":217189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:39:22.000Z","msg":"出院後死唔計數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a486fb27cd315eb6096bbbb9acd8d684dc1f718d","tid":1910568,"uid":43687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:41:08.000Z","msg":"求上天保佑香港黎多59個案例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882d5a4814f4d1985e8157cd7ce3df3102858b62","tid":1910568,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:42:46.000Z","msg":"唔係死喺入面已經係黨給予你嘅恩賜啦，至少畀你見幾日屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea797e85c8cca4ee50b29939adad5fc7e3bf4943","tid":1910568,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />【武漢一方艙醫院發布緊急通知：出院患者中復發者較多，擬出院病友需加做病毒抗體檢查】#方艙醫院出院需加做病毒抗體檢查#3月4日晚，武漢市江岸方艙醫院一名負責人向記者證實，江岸方艙醫院發布了一份《緊急通知》：根據市防疫指揮部最新通報，近期出院患者中復發者較多，導致患者重新入院治療。為了減少病情復發，確保大家徹底治愈，達到&ldquo;零回頭&rdquo;目標，經醫院研究決定，即日對所有在艙擬出院病友抽血加做病毒抗體Ig-M與Ig-G的檢查，確保病友完全康復出院，敬請各位病友配合。上述檢查將從明天（3月5日）開始。該負責人表示，市防疫指揮部通知他們，有患者出艙以後出現核酸檢測轉陽的情況，所以為了患者徹底治好，加做病毒抗體Ig-M與Ig-G的檢查。 &ldquo;加做抗體（出結果）很快，明天開始（給患者）做，明天晚上就可以出結果。&rdquo;該負責人說，為了使患者徹底治愈，江岸方艙醫院決定採取上述措施。至於其他方艙醫院是否也會加做抗體檢查，該負責人表示尚不清楚。"},{"pid":"8d6ffd3a89ef447a663b9aa1a56d8cea8b0ddec5","tid":1910568,"uid":327462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VYH1BX7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVYH1BX7.jpg&h=072e322f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff50be91c4db7b7d08771fb3f8431db5c317fbdb","tid":1910568,"uid":327462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7715c9e4d69388c88628793ab6b374d61cfef06","tid":1910568,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:31:59.000Z","msg":"個名有兩個字一樣都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T18:46:25.000Z","msg":"下一個被肺炎死嘅應該叫李文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fe11838b78d2df6ca17d18034dea1bbca87d09","tid":1910568,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60c61912558cae01ae418c50b0ff33a6ca4ca872","tid":1910568,"uid":342527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"re